    <sampling_method>Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Diagnosis of HIV-1 infection during participation in any Microbicide Trials Network
             (MTN) clinical trial (including HPTN 035 and HPTN 059), according to the HIV testing
             algorithm of the parent MTN trial

          -  Parent or guardian willing to provide informed consent, if applicable

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Any condition that, in the opinion of the investigator, makes participation in the
             study unsafe or interferes with the study
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
